PREREQUISITES
  Java version 11.0.11
  Jenkins 
  Docker
  Docker-compose
  Nginx.
  
Write a Docker file.
    create a workDir /app
    To get the latest code from the current directory use . /app
    To run the node app use npm install
    For exporting the server in 3000 port use Export 3000
    
 write a Docker-compose.yml file
  Go to the path docker-compose.yml file
 
 Install Jenkins
  Make the configuration of Jenkins as required.
  
Run a pipeline script in Jenkins 
 path to pipeline script is jenkins.groovy.
 
Install Nginx 
set the configuaration in nginx like port number.
  
 The app will run finally on the nodejs port  3000 and nginx port.
